{
  "stem": "8784.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And vital in all this is that work force that is so highly skilled that now is trapped in Gross Rosen and is also trapped in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The women are trapped in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And evidently, he pulled off the-- the whole scheme that in Gross Rosen they carefully called our names and loaded us on our-- on the railroad-- in the cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And as the movie shows, the women were similarly loaded on cattle cars and shipped out of Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Also, at times-- at that time during the war, I thought that the ladies out of Auschwitz were walking on foot towards our camp.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But whether they walked part of the trip and part of the trip they were on the railroad, I don't know at this point anymore unless I would verify it with somebody that was in that group with the ladies.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We did, after a-- after a few days on sidings again being shipped-- being shifted from one track to another, we arrived in-- still in October of 1944, we arrived at this town of Brunnlitz, where Oskar Schindler was-- was awaiting us.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He was in the camp already.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He had created some accommodations for us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He had barbed wire surrounding the premises.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "If I recollected correctly, the barbed wires were no longer the same fearful barbed wires that we had in the other concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They did not seem to have the watchtowers, the fearful watchtowers that were in the other concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But nevertheless, there were some barbed wires surrounding this linen-- this old linen factory, and we began work at that time in that factory.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Schindler began to build his offices.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I was again employed as a cabinet maker-carpenter and worked with a bunch of people that were doing carpentry like myself.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
